---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Virginia Page & Co. Hair Studio"
  description="Privacy Policy for Virginia Page & Co. Hair Studio. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <section class="pt-16 pb-24 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <span class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-[--color-gold] mb-4 block">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="display-lg mb-8" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-[--color-taupe] mb-12">Last updated: February 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-12 text-[--color-charcoal] leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-[--color-taupe] mb-4">
            When you book an appointment or contact us, we may collect:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-[--color-taupe]">
            <li>Name, email address, and phone number</li>
            <li>Appointment preferences and service history</li>
            <li>Payment information (processed securely by our scheduling provider)</li>
            <li>Any information you provide in messages or forms</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="text-[--color-taupe] mb-4">
            Our website uses the following third-party services that may collect data:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-[--color-taupe]">
            <li><strong>Acuity Scheduling</strong> &mdash; Online appointment booking and payment processing</li>
            <li><strong>Google Maps</strong> &mdash; Embedded map on our Contact page</li>
            <li><strong>Instagram</strong> &mdash; Links to our social media portfolio</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-[--color-taupe] mt-4">
            Each service operates under its own privacy policy. We encourage you to review their policies for details on how they handle your data.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-[--color-taupe]">
            <li>To schedule and manage your appointments</li>
            <li>To communicate with you about your bookings</li>
            <li>To improve our services and website experience</li>
            <li>To respond to your inquiries</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">Data Sharing</h2>
          <p class="text-[--color-taupe]">
            We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties. We only share your data with the service providers listed above as necessary to operate our business.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="text-[--color-taupe]">
            We retain your appointment and contact information for as long as necessary to provide our services and comply with legal obligations. You may request deletion of your data at any time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-[--color-taupe] mb-4">You have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-[--color-taupe]">
            <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Opt out of marketing communications</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-display);">Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-[--color-taupe]">
            For questions about this policy or to exercise your data rights, contact us at
            <a href="mailto:vacohairstudio@gmail.com" class="text-[--color-gold] hover:underline">vacohairstudio@gmail.com</a>
            or call <a href="tel:9196718353" class="text-[--color-gold] hover:underline">(919) 671-8353</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
